<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٩٢١ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6085">مُسَدَّدٌ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةَ </a>أَخْبَرَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةُ: </a>أَنَّ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسًا </a>حَدَّثَهُمْ قَالَ: <span class="c2">«رَخَّصَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> لِعَبْدِ الرَّحْمَنِ بْنِ عَوْفٍ وَالزُّبَيْرِ بْنِ الْعَوَّامِ فِي حَرِيرٍ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>